On the basis of the above leaf counts, in which a total of 951 specimens were examined and counted, the following species are considered the dominants of the

type Lance flora as a whole:

Araucarites longifolia Dryophyllum subfalcatum Platanophyllum montanum Fraxinus leii

Salix laneensis Viburnum marginatum Sequoia dakotensis ’ Cornophyllum wardii Vitis stantoni Pistia corrugata

These 10 species represent about 69 per cent of all the specimens encountered in the collections from the nine localities listed.
